dict.string: The type of the shape among rectangle (2), sphere (1), polygon (2), polygonZ (1), capsule (2), torus (2), banana (3) , dice (4), strip (3), periodic (3), ellipse (3), cylinder (2), cylinderZ (3), cylinderP (2) and ring (2). Each of these shapes have (1..3) parameters that are set upon a 'new' command.
